text: Zorro Rides Again is a Western movie from 1937. It is about a villain trying to steal a new railroad. It was directed by William Witney and John English. It stars John Carroll, Reed Howes, Duncan Renaldo, Noah Beery Sr., Edmund Cobb, Nigel De Brulier. ==Other websites== * * Category:1937 movies Category:1930s epic movies Category:1930s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by William Witney Category:Movies set in California Category:Movies directed by John English
